				<div type="section"><head>About the Romantic Pedagogies Commons
					Series</head>
				
					<p rend="noCount">The <title level="j">Romantic Circles Pedagogies Commons</title> is a peer-reviewed online journal dedicated to the presentation of essays about teaching that offer sample teaching materials as well, from printable handouts to "digital-born" teaching materials.</p></div>
				
